{
  "video_id": "BGAv_5hPDbc",
  "title": "Chapter 8",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 233.0,
      "end_time": 2400.0,
      "text": ">> In chapter 8, we&#39;re going to look at contractual capacity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 2400.0,
      "end_time": 5699.0,
      "text": "legality, and enforceability."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 5700.0,
      "end_time": 7800.0,
      "text": "Contractual capacity is the legal ability to enter"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 7800.0,
      "end_time": 10100.0,
      "text": "into a contractual relationship."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 10100.0,
      "end_time": 13000.0,
      "text": "A person who is determined by court to be mentally incompetent"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 13000.0,
      "end_time": 15767.0,
      "text": "can&#39;t enter into a valid contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 15767.0,
      "end_time": 17933.0,
      "text": "In other situations, the capacity may exist"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 17934.0,
      "end_time": 20433.0,
      "text": "but the contract isn&#39;t legally binding."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 20433.0,
      "end_time": 24433.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ll take a look at those situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 24433.0,
      "end_time": 29467.0,
      "text": "Minors can enter into contracts, generally at the age of 18,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29467.0,
      "end_time": 32467.0,
      "text": "a person in emancipated and has a legal capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 32467.0,
      "end_time": 35600.0,
      "text": "to enter any contract that an adult can."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 37333.0,
      "end_time": 40567.0,
      "text": "However, a contract entered into by a minor is voidable"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40567.0,
      "end_time": 43467.0,
      "text": "at the option of that minor and can be disaffirmed."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 43467.0,
      "end_time": 48567.0,
      "text": "\"Disaffirm\" means \"to avoid a contract.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 48567.0,
      "end_time": 51600.0,
      "text": "The Majority Rule is that the minor has an obligation"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51600.0,
      "end_time": 55500.0,
      "text": "only to return the goods or other considerations"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 55500.0,
      "end_time": 57934.0,
      "text": "subject to the contract, provided the goods"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57934.0,
      "end_time": 61567.0,
      "text": "are still in the possession of the minor."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61567.0,
      "end_time": 65734.0,
      "text": "Minority Rule is that the minor must restore the adult"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65734.0,
      "end_time": 68967.0,
      "text": "to the position held before the contract was made."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68967.0,
      "end_time": 74266.0,
      "text": "In other words, most states don&#39;t require the minor"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74266.0,
      "end_time": 76667.0,
      "text": "to make the other party whole--"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76667.0,
      "end_time": 79266.0,
      "text": "just return whatever they have left."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83567.0,
      "end_time": 86500.0,
      "text": "There are some exceptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86500.0,
      "end_time": 89100.0,
      "text": "Generally, a minor can disaffirm a contract,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89100.0,
      "end_time": 91567.0,
      "text": "even if they misrepresent their age."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91567.0,
      "end_time": 95866.0,
      "text": "However, there are some states that prohibit disaffirmance"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95867.0,
      "end_time": 100200.0,
      "text": "and hold a minor liable once the minor commits fraud"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100200.0,
      "end_time": 103200.0,
      "text": "by misrepresenting their age."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103200.0,
      "end_time": 106233.0,
      "text": "Contracts for necessaries-- things like food, clothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 106233.0,
      "end_time": 108500.0,
      "text": "and shelter-- a minor could avoid"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108500.0,
      "end_time": 112333.0,
      "text": "but somebody will be held responsible for it."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 112333.0,
      "end_time": 115867.0,
      "text": "A contract could be ratified."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115867.0,
      "end_time": 121660.0,
      "text": "\"Ratified\" means to go ahead with a contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 121660.0,
      "end_time": 122867.0,
      "text": "instead of avoiding it."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122867.0,
      "end_time": 125333.0,
      "text": "And the author says it occurs when a minor"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125333.0,
      "end_time": 127133.0,
      "text": "on or after reaching the age of the majority."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 127133.0,
      "end_time": 133132.0,
      "text": "Well, technically, they would no longer be a minor so--"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133133.0,
      "end_time": 136200.0,
      "text": "a minor who enters into a contract can ratify it"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 136200.0,
      "end_time": 138132.0,
      "text": "once they reach the age of majority"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138133.0,
      "end_time": 141330.0,
      "text": "or for a reasonable period of time afterwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 141330.0,
      "end_time": 143166.0,
      "text": "Now, that could be expressed or implied."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 143166.0,
      "end_time": 147133.0,
      "text": "They could say that they don&#39;t wish to avoid the contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 147133.0,
      "end_time": 152533.0,
      "text": "or they could impliedly ratify it by just staying in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 152533.0,
      "end_time": 156500.0,
      "text": "Generally, parents don&#39;t have a liability for contracts entered"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 156500.0,
      "end_time": 162367.0,
      "text": "into by minors unless they were required to co-sign."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163633.0,
      "end_time": 167166.0,
      "text": "Intoxicated persons could avoid a contract if they lack capacity"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 167166.0,
      "end_time": 170500.0,
      "text": "at the time the contract is made."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 172867.0,
      "end_time": 176667.0,
      "text": "If they still have the capacity to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 176667.0,
      "end_time": 178667.0,
      "text": "what they were doing, it would be valid."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 181333.0,
      "end_time": 183667.0,
      "text": "One thing they could do is, after they sober up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 183667.0,
      "end_time": 185900.0,
      "text": "they could decide they want to remain in the contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185900.0,
      "end_time": 188800.0,
      "text": "So \"voidable\" means \"at the option of the person"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188800.0,
      "end_time": 190800.0,
      "text": "\"who was intoxicated at the time.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 196200.0,
      "end_time": 198700.0,
      "text": "If a person has been determined to be mentally incompetent"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 198700.0,
      "end_time": 201632.0,
      "text": "by a court, and a guardian has been appointed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 201633.0,
      "end_time": 205934.0,
      "text": "then any attempt for them to enter into contract is void."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 205934.0,
      "end_time": 212266.0,
      "text": "If the person hasn&#39;t been declared to be incompetent"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 212266.0,
      "end_time": 215799.0,
      "text": "by a court, but does lack the mental capacity at the time"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 215800.0,
      "end_time": 220166.0,
      "text": "they entered into a contract, the contract is voidable."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 221433.0,
      "end_time": 225000.0,
      "text": "If they did understand the nature and effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 225000.0,
      "end_time": 231500.0,
      "text": "of the contract, then the contract is valid."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 231500.0,
      "end_time": 234000.0,
      "text": "Sometimes, this could be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 234000.0,
      "end_time": 237767.0,
      "text": "depending on the person&#39;s mental state--"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 237767.0,
      "end_time": 240400.0,
      "text": "in other words, if they have a lucid interval,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 240400.0,
      "end_time": 243567.0,
      "text": "if they understand what they&#39;re doing, it would be valid."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 243567.0,
      "end_time": 247967.0,
      "text": "If, at the time, they lacked the capacity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 247967.0,
      "end_time": 249266.0,
      "text": "then it would be voidable."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 252266.0,
      "end_time": 254433.0,
      "text": "Look at the legality of the contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 254433.0,
      "end_time": 255533.0,
      "text": "For a contract to be enforceable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 255533.0,
      "end_time": 258466.0,
      "text": "it must be for a legal purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 258466.0,
      "end_time": 260933.0,
      "text": "You could have a clause in the contract that&#39;s illegal"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 260934.00000000003,
      "end_time": 267266.0,
      "text": "but the rest of the contract could be legal and enforceable."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 267266.0,
      "end_time": 271500.0,
      "text": "Were a contract to commit a tort or a crime, it would be illegal."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 272934.0,
      "end_time": 275400.0,
      "text": "Contracts contrary to statute."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 275400.0,
      "end_time": 277633.0,
      "text": "If there&#39;s a federal or a state law that prohibits something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 277633.0,
      "end_time": 280633.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t contract to do it and it would be void."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 280633.0,
      "end_time": 284332.0,
      "text": "In other words, it would be not a contract from the start."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 284333.0,
      "end_time": 287834.0,
      "text": "Usary-- which means charging an excessive interest rate"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 287834.0,
      "end_time": 291867.0,
      "text": "above the law-- would not be enforced."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 291867.0,
      "end_time": 293967.0,
      "text": "Gambling would be another example of a contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 293967.0,
      "end_time": 298366.0,
      "text": "that wouldn&#39;t be enforced unless of course it&#39;s sanctioned"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 298367.0,
      "end_time": 300133.0,
      "text": "by the government."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 300133.0,
      "end_time": 305532.0,
      "text": "In licensing statutes-- attempt to enter into a contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 305533.0,
      "end_time": 308767.0,
      "text": "without proper license could effect"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 308767.0,
      "end_time": 311200.0,
      "text": "the enforceability of the contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 311200.0,
      "end_time": 312834.0,
      "text": "If the purpose of the licensing statute"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 312834.0,
      "end_time": 315330.0,
      "text": "is simply to generate revenue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 315330.0,
      "end_time": 317967.0,
      "text": "generally the courts will give a remedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 317967.0,
      "end_time": 320433.0,
      "text": "However, if it&#39;s to protect the public safety--"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 320433.0,
      "end_time": 324633.0,
      "text": "for example, licensing for attorneys, doctors, etcetera--"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 324633.0,
      "end_time": 328320.0,
      "text": "then you&#39;re not going to be able to enter into contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 328330.0,
      "end_time": 330300.0,
      "text": "without that license."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 331934.0,
      "end_time": 335400.0,
      "text": "Contracts that are contrary to public policy--"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 335400.0,
      "end_time": 340633.0,
      "text": "such as a restraint of trade-- are generally void."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 340633.0,
      "end_time": 344467.0,
      "text": "However, a covenant not to compete could be enforceable"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 344467.0,
      "end_time": 348866.0,
      "text": "if it&#39;s geographic terms are reasonable"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 348867.0,
      "end_time": 353800.0,
      "text": "and the duration of time is reasonable."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 353800.0,
      "end_time": 355266.0,
      "text": "A contract may not be enforced"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 355266.0,
      "end_time": 356967.0,
      "text": "if it&#39;s procedurally unconscionable--"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 356967.0,
      "end_time": 361660.0,
      "text": "meaning it has inconspicuous or small print"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 361660.0,
      "end_time": 365166.0,
      "text": "or difficult legalese,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 365166.0,
      "end_time": 367933.0,
      "text": "that would depend on the party&#39;s lack of knowledge."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 367934.0,
      "end_time": 370433.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s also substantive unconscionability"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 370433.0,
      "end_time": 375567.0,
      "text": "where the terms or conditions surrounding the contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 375567.0,
      "end_time": 378500.0,
      "text": "are oppressive or overly harsh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 378500.0,
      "end_time": 382233.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t provide a party with any remedy whatsoever."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 382233.0,
      "end_time": 383934.0,
      "text": "The court may not enforce it."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 383934.0,
      "end_time": 387233.0,
      "text": "Exculpatory clauses are clauses that release a party"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 387233.0,
      "end_time": 390166.0,
      "text": "from liability in the event of some kind of injury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 390166.0,
      "end_time": 393734.0,
      "text": "regardless of who&#39;s at fault."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 393734.0,
      "end_time": 396767.0,
      "text": "The court will enforce them if it&#39;s not contrary"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 396767.0,
      "end_time": 400100.0,
      "text": "to public policy, not ambiguous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 400100.0,
      "end_time": 403867.0,
      "text": "and doesn&#39;t shield the party from intentional conduct."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 403867.0,
      "end_time": 408660.0,
      "text": "So if there was a clause that said you could escape liability"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 408660.0,
      "end_time": 410320.0,
      "text": "even if you committed some intentional act"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 410330.0,
      "end_time": 415330.0,
      "text": "against someone else, the courts generally won&#39;t enforce those."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 415330.0,
      "end_time": 420300.0,
      "text": "As we said earlier, illegal contracts are void."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 420300.0,
      "end_time": 422667.0,
      "text": "Neither party would be able to collect"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 422667.0,
      "end_time": 425133.0,
      "text": "or recover in that situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 425133.0,
      "end_time": 431532.0,
      "text": "There are some situations where the court has granted a remedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 431533.0,
      "end_time": 433667.0,
      "text": "If there were some justifiable ignorance of fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 433667.0,
      "end_time": 435866.0,
      "text": "on an innocent party&#39;s behalf,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 435867.0,
      "end_time": 442533.0,
      "text": "if one of the parties was part of a protected class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 442533.0,
      "end_time": 445433.0,
      "text": "if there was a chance to withdraw from an illegal agreement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 445433.0,
      "end_time": 447700.0,
      "text": "if part of the contract which was illegal"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 447700.0,
      "end_time": 451300.0,
      "text": "could be severed from the legal part,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 451300.0,
      "end_time": 453734.0,
      "text": "or the contract was entered into under fraud,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 453734.0,
      "end_time": 456967.0,
      "text": "duress, or undue influence."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 458330.0,
      "end_time": 462533.0,
      "text": "Mistake could allow a party to avoid a contract."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 462533.0,
      "end_time": 464667.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re talking about a mistake of fact, not value."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 464667.0,
      "end_time": 467700.0,
      "text": "Not paying too much for something."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 467700.0,
      "end_time": 469265.0,
      "text": "If it&#39;s a unilateral mistake,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 469266.0,
      "end_time": 471567.0,
      "text": "generally the courts won&#39;t allow that party"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 471567.0,
      "end_time": 475500.0,
      "text": "to get out of the contract unless the other party"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 475500.0,
      "end_time": 476867.0,
      "text": "knew they were making that mistake"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 476867.0,
      "end_time": 480533.0,
      "text": "or it was something like a typo."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 480533.0,
      "end_time": 483533.0,
      "text": "However, courts do allow the parties to back out"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 483533.0,
      "end_time": 486367.0,
      "text": "if there&#39;s a bi-lateral or mutual mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 486367.0,
      "end_time": 489533.0,
      "text": "This would be basically the parties not agreeing"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 489533.0,
      "end_time": 495800.0,
      "text": "to the same thing as the result of a mistake."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 495800.0,
      "end_time": 499266.0,
      "text": "Fraudulent misrepresentation may make a contract voidable"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 499266.0,
      "end_time": 501533.0,
      "text": "by the innocent party."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 501533.0,
      "end_time": 505367.0,
      "text": "It requires misrepresentation of a material fact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 505367.0,
      "end_time": 507133.0,
      "text": "an intent to deceive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 507133.0,
      "end_time": 508866.0,
      "text": "a reliance on that misrepresentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 508867.0,
      "end_time": 511934.0,
      "text": "and an injury to the innocent party."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 511934.0,
      "end_time": 513300.0,
      "text": "These are different ways that you"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 513299.0,
      "end_time": 515567.0,
      "text": "could have a misrepresentation of material fact."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 515567.0,
      "end_time": 518330.0,
      "text": "It could be how the parties acted."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 518330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 522834.00000000006,
      "text": "It could be an \"expert\" opinion--"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 522832.99999999994,
      "end_time": 528566.0,
      "text": "typically, opinions by others would not be actionable."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 528567.0,
      "end_time": 534834.0,
      "text": "It could be by law or by silence, even."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 534834.0,
      "end_time": 536632.0,
      "text": "The party could fail to disclose something"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 536633.0,
      "end_time": 539700.0,
      "text": "that they have a duty to disclose."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 539700.0,
      "end_time": 542867.0,
      "text": "For example, if they have a fiduciary relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 542867.0,
      "end_time": 546867.0,
      "text": "and they fail to disclose material facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 546867.0,
      "end_time": 553733.0,
      "text": "The intent to deceive is required-- a person does it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 553734.0,
      "end_time": 556367.0,
      "text": "makes the fraudulent misrepresentation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 556367.0,
      "end_time": 558666.0,
      "text": "knowing the fact is not true"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 558667.0,
      "end_time": 563633.0,
      "text": "or is reckless in their statements about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 567330.0,
      "end_time": 568767.0,
      "text": "The other party-- the deceived party--"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 568767.0,
      "end_time": 572330.0,
      "text": "must justify and be reliant on the representation."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 572330.0,
      "end_time": 580500.0,
      "text": "If they knew it not to be true, that wouldn&#39;t be justifiable."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 580500.0,
      "end_time": 582300.0,
      "text": "And there has to be an actual injury,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 582300.0,
      "end_time": 583967.0,
      "text": "so you could say something that&#39;s not true"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 583967.0,
      "end_time": 586834.0,
      "text": "and if the other party relied on it but wasn&#39;t injured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 586834.0,
      "end_time": 589900.0,
      "text": "that wouldn&#39;t fraudulent misrepresentation."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 589900.0,
      "end_time": 592165.0,
      "text": "However, no proof of injury is required when the action"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 592166.0,
      "end_time": 593600.0,
      "text": "is to rescind the contract--"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 593600.0,
      "end_time": 598433.0,
      "text": "so, if you&#39;re just asking to back out."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 598433.0,
      "end_time": 602100.0,
      "text": "Undue influence is when there&#39;s a special relationship"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 602100.0,
      "end_time": 605433.0,
      "text": "between the parties."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 605433.0,
      "end_time": 607967.0,
      "text": "In that situation, the contract would lack voluntary consent"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 607967.0,
      "end_time": 609834.0,
      "text": "and would be voidable."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 609834.0,
      "end_time": 611500.0,
      "text": "An example might be \"attorney, client,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 611500.0,
      "end_time": 613233.0,
      "text": "\"guardian, ward.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 613233.0,
      "end_time": 616800.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s presumed that the weaker party"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 616800.0,
      "end_time": 618199.0,
      "text": "would be talked into doing something"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 618200.0,
      "end_time": 621900.0,
      "text": "that wasn&#39;t beneficial to him or herself."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 621900.0,
      "end_time": 624100.0,
      "text": "Duress would be physically forcing"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 624100.0,
      "end_time": 628767.0,
      "text": "or threatening physical force."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 628767.0,
      "end_time": 631433.0,
      "text": "That would make a contract voidable."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 631433.0,
      "end_time": 634266.0,
      "text": "Threat of civil suit or not getting a good deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 634266.0,
      "end_time": 637967.0,
      "text": "Economic duress generally isn&#39;t sufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 640200.0,
      "end_time": 643433.0,
      "text": "In some cases, another defense to enforceability"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 643433.0,
      "end_time": 645000.0,
      "text": "is the form that the contract is."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 645000.0,
      "end_time": 647967.0,
      "text": "Some contracts required to be in writing"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 647967.0,
      "end_time": 649467.0,
      "text": "and signed by the party"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 649467.0,
      "end_time": 652667.0,
      "text": "against whom you&#39;re going to enforce it."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 652667.0,
      "end_time": 655567.0,
      "text": "Here are the-- this is the statute of frauds, basically."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 655567.0,
      "end_time": 658133.0,
      "text": "Here are the five areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 658133.0,
      "end_time": 662367.0,
      "text": "Contracts involving the interest in land, the \"One-Year\" Rule,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 662367.0,
      "end_time": 664834.0,
      "text": "collateral or secondary contracts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 664834.0,
      "end_time": 666800.0,
      "text": "promises made in consideration of marriage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 666800.0,
      "end_time": 670666.0,
      "text": "contracts for the sale of goods priced at $500 or more."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 670667.0,
      "end_time": 672330.0,
      "text": "So, when we say \"interest in land,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 672330.0,
      "end_time": 677330.0,
      "text": "we would mean land contract, leases, sale of land."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 677330.0,
      "end_time": 678934.0,
      "text": "The \"One-Year\" basically says a contract"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 678934.0,
      "end_time": 683199.0,
      "text": "that cannot by, its performed terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 683200.0,
      "end_time": 687900.0,
      "text": "be performed within a one year, need to be in writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 687900.0,
      "end_time": 691165.0,
      "text": "Collateral or secondary contracts mean co-signing."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 691166.0,
      "end_time": 693233.0,
      "text": "A co-signature should be in writing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 693233.0,
      "end_time": 700266.0,
      "text": "unless the purpose of the oral guarantee to pay the debt"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 700266.0,
      "end_time": 705333.0,
      "text": "to someone else is to benefit yourself."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 705333.0,
      "end_time": 707900.0,
      "text": "Prenuptial agreements, promises made"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 707900.0,
      "end_time": 710660.0,
      "text": "in contemplation of marriage."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 710660.0,
      "end_time": 715567.0,
      "text": "And contracts for the sale of goods priced at $500 or more."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 715567.0,
      "end_time": 717100.0,
      "text": "So, if you were to look at a quiz question"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 717100.0,
      "end_time": 721633.0,
      "text": "and it was talking about an oral agreement for more than that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 721633.0,
      "end_time": 725400.0,
      "text": "then the statute of frauds would require it to be in writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 725400.0,
      "end_time": 726867.0,
      "text": "There are some exceptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 726867.0,
      "end_time": 728867.0,
      "text": "You know, the idea is that you wouldn&#39;t have anything"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 728867.0,
      "end_time": 730800.0,
      "text": "to prove that there was an agreement."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 730800.0,
      "end_time": 733500.0,
      "text": "However, you could substitute that with partial performance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 733500.0,
      "end_time": 735330.0,
      "text": "maybe somebody&#39;s already shipped goods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 735330.0,
      "end_time": 737500.0,
      "text": "the other party&#39;s paid part of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 737500.0,
      "end_time": 741934.0,
      "text": "An admission that there is an agreement in court."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 743133.0,
      "end_time": 745934.0,
      "text": "Promissory estoppel, which we&#39;ve talked about before."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 745934.0,
      "end_time": 749199.0,
      "text": "Basically, the idea that although the whole agreement"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 749200.0,
      "end_time": 752600.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t in writing, but there was a promise to the other party"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 752600.0,
      "end_time": 757967.0,
      "text": "and justifiably relied on, and other special exceptions"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 757967.0,
      "end_time": 761233.0,
      "text": "under the UCC."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 761233.0,
      "end_time": 763300.0,
      "text": "The writing doesn&#39;t have to be too complex."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 763300.0,
      "end_time": 766199.0,
      "text": "It just could be a written memorandum"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 766200.0,
      "end_time": 767967.0,
      "text": "or electronic signed by the party"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 767967.0,
      "end_time": 770433.0,
      "text": "against whom enforcement is sought."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 770433.0,
      "end_time": 773734.0,
      "text": "It could be a fax, it could be an email."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 773734.0,
      "end_time": 775900.0,
      "text": "Basically, it just has to have the essential terms."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 775900.0,
      "end_time": 780867.0,
      "text": "Quantity needs to be in there."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 780867.0,
      "end_time": 782333.0,
      "text": "We mentioned signature of the party"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 782333.0,
      "end_time": 784632.0,
      "text": "against who you&#39;re trying to enforce it."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 784633.0,
      "end_time": 786800.0,
      "text": "Who the parties."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 786800.0,
      "end_time": 788400.0,
      "text": "What the contract&#39;s about-- the subject matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 788400.0,
      "end_time": 791834.0,
      "text": "And what consideration is being exchanged."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 791834.0,
      "end_time": 794632.0,
      "text": "In the sale of land, it needs to state the price"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 794633.0,
      "end_time": 798166.0,
      "text": "and description with sufficient clarity."
    }
  ]
}